<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Bangtik a le lul zing thisan,
 Tun kei dingin a lul;
 Thisan chun lauh, ginlah apat,
 Ka thagau a chawlh sak.

[V2]
 Aw thisan lui maktak a luong,
 Hukdampa nak a chun;
 Van chana ka la hizing ding,
 &quot;Thisan lul thisan lul.&quot;

[V3]
 2. &quot;A ngawlnau leh gitlohna haw,
 Hezing zing ta puong ka;
 Ka Chapa thisan luon ziekin&quot;
 Pathien Thu chun a tii.

[V4]
 3. Gitlohna ka hetzing haw chun,
 Ei sulau thei puon au;
 Thisan lul chun a khuh vek tai,
 Ka gitloh a lamang.

[V5]
 4. Ka sapum hatlo hin natna,
 A thuok pai mai theia;
 Thisan ah chawl leng bangti phet,
 A muongin ka thi dem.</lyrics>
<title>THE PRECIOUS BLOOD</title>
</song>